Skills

I’m a full-stack developer with expert level experience in databases, server-side business logic processing and client-side user interfaces.

At a high level, these are the tools of my trade.

  • Microsoft Azure, DevOps, Apps & Infra
  • C# / .NET Core / Asp.NET Core / SignalR
  • Angular / React / TypeScript / Javascript / NodeJS
  • Azure Sql Server / Azure Synapse / Azure CosmosDb / MongoDb
  • Git / GitHub / BitBucket
